<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Detalle del Condicionante</title>
    <!-- Agregar enlace a Bootstrap CSS desde un CDN -->
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    />
    <!-- Enlace al archivo CSS personalizado -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container mt-5">
      <div class="row mb-4">
        <div class="col-8">
          <h3 class="mb-0">
            Detalle <%- (condicionante.Type == 3 || condicionante.Type == "Advertencia") ? 'de la advertencia' : 'del condicionante' %>
          </h3>
        </div>
        <div class="col-4 d-flex flex-row-reverse"><a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Volver a la lista</a></div>
      </div>

      <ul class="list-group">
        <li class="list-group-item d-flex flex-row">
          <strong>Version</strong> <%= condicionante.Status %>
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item d-flex flex-row">
          <strong>AVMId</strong> <%= condicionante.StandarizedKey %>
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item d-flex flex-row">
          <strong>Id</strong> <%= condicionante.TinsaKey %>
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item d-flex flex-row">
          <strong>Risk</strong> <%- (condicionante.Type == 2  || condicionante.Type == 1 || condicionante.Type == "Condicionante") ? '<span class="badge bg-danger">High</span>' : (condicionante.Type == 3 || condicionante.Type == "Advertencia") ? '<span class="badge bg-warning">Low</span>' : (condicionante.Type == 1) ? '<span class="badge bg-dark">Lowest</span>' : '<span class="badge bg-success">Info</span>' %>
          &nbsp; (<%= condicionante.Type %>)
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="alert alert-warning mt-3" role="alert">
       <b>Importante:</b> Esta explicación <%- (condicionante.Type == 3 || condicionante.Type == "Advertencia") ? 'de la advertencia' : 'del condicionante' %> tiene como objetivo acercar de manera simple y directa los aspectos más relevantes del informe.
       Sin embargo, es esencial consultar el informe de tasación completo para obtener una comprensión detallada y técnica de cada punto.
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
          <ul class="list-group">
            <li class="list-group-item"><h5>Español</h5></li>
            <li class="list-group-item d-flex flex-row">
              <strong>Texto original</strong> 
              <p><%- condicionante.Original %></p>
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item d-flex flex-row">
              <strong>Resumen</strong> <%- condicionante.Summary %>
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item d-flex flex-row">
              <strong>Detalles</strong> <%- condicionante.Details %>
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item d-flex flex-row">
              <strong>Beneficios</strong> <%- condicionante.Benefits %>
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item d-flex flex-row">
              <strong>Acciones</strong> <%- (condicionante.Actions !== 'nulll') ? '' : condicionante.Actions %>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 mt-3">
          <ul class="list-group translation">
            <li class="list-group-item"><h5>English</h5></li>
            <li class="list-group-item d-flex flex-row">
              <strong>Summary</strong>
              <textarea name="" class="form-control">The lease agreement is required for the appraisal</textarea>
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item d-flex flex-row">
              <strong>Details</strong>
              <textarea name="" class="form-control">The lease agreement provides specific details about the terms and conditions under which a property is rented. This information is essential to understand the rights and obligations of the parties and can influence the valuation of the property.</textarea>
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item d-flex flex-row">
              <strong>Benefits</strong>
              <textarea name="" class="form-control">A current and valid contract can add value and certainty to the property by ensuring future income and stabilizing its use.</textarea>
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item d-flex flex-row">
              <strong>Actions</strong>
              <textarea name="" class="form-control">Provide a current copy of the lease agreement to ensure an accurate valuation.</textarea>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
